        <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✓ Eat These</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Almonds, bananas, oat bars, dark chocolate, hard-boiled eggs, trail mix, wholegrain sandwiches</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-red-500/30 bg-red-950/10">
        <p class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✗ Avoid These</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Sweets, fizzy drinks, heavy meals, excessive caffeine, fast food, energy drinks after 3pm</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>Many top players bring a tournament food kit with pre-portioned snacks. Heavy meals redirect blood to digestion and cause afternoon drowsiness — the dreaded "Round 5 slump" that costs games.</p>

